nt color=#333333>(10/28/03 12:38 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/ffaeryfirealongthenightshorefrm7.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=54>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Ex Oblivio</span><hr size=1> Tehn stood solitary on a road floating in darkness.  Cords of pathways surged around him, like so many threads that create a tapestry.  As they wove, the patterns only created more chaos, and each degree of organization that seemed to be forming only added to the murky obsidion of endless night and confusion.  As he stood there, a mighty stone highway cleaved through his walkway, sundering it in front of him, leaving no way to progress, and somehow, no way behind either.  As the darkness twined, a ray of non-darkness shot out from in front of him, and seemed to reel in a feeble dirt trail, merely dust scattered haphazardly, floating in the nothingness and winding through others that seemed much safer, yet unavailable.  He began the trail as something began to follow.  Tehn knew he couldn't look and stay aright, but as he continued along the path which followed no rules of physics or euclidian existence, they seemed to grow in number.  The path went on endlessly, and endlessly they grew in number behind him.  As the path looped around a particularly astounding causeway, Tehn saw thousands of small orbs tailing behind, all colors and beyond.  He turned around, and one drifted into his hand, a small world of blues and oranges, beautiful yet somehow desolate.  As he turned around, the mighty doors of the library were before him, part of the causeway.  As he walked through, he became horrified as behind him all the paths of existence burst into silent pale violet flames, and the murky ashes began to soar towards him, and coalesce on his skin, hardening, stiffening his joints.  The orbs were gone, and as the armor formed around him, he tried to flee the ash which was continuing to group, yet it was paralyzing him.... <p>______________________________<br>
