us? Otherwise we're in for a rather interesting fight, especially since I don't know how to combat magic.&quot; Concluding his idea Sparrow looked at the faces of his party in hope that someone had an idea or at least some knowledge of how to counter the magical power thay where soon to be up against.<br>
